"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:4.5.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">4.5.2</span> 標題：內袍、束腰長襯衫、襯衫（tunic, shirt）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： כֻּתֹּנֶת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kutoneth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:4\">EXO 28:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:39\">EXO 28:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:40\">EXO 28:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:5\">EXO 29:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:8\">EXO 29:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:27\">EXO 39:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:14\">EXO 40:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:7\">LEV 8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:13\">LEV 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:5\">LEV 10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:4\">LEV 16:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra2:69\">EZR 2:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:69\">NEH 7:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:71\">NEH 7:71</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： χιτών</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： chitōn)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:63\">MRK 14:63</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0039_priest_tunic.jpg\" alt=\"身穿長袍的祭司\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">身穿長袍的祭司 (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>內袍是大祭司及一同供職的祭司穿著的另一件內衣。內袍穿在短褲外面，但從腰部以上是貼身的，外面套著外袍。內袍是一種幾乎長及腳踝的襯衫，大概是長袖的，用細麻布織成，可能是套頭式的，用一條繫在腰部的帶子來扎緊。另參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">6.3 襯衫、束腰長襯衫(shirt, tunic)&lt;REALIA:6.3&gt;</a> 。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希伯來文<em>kutoneth</em> 一般指男女穿著的日常衣服，很可能是一種「襯衫」。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 將其譯成“coat”（「外套」；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:4\">EXO 28:4</a> ）可能會誤導讀者，因為這件衣服不是外衣，而是在其他衣物裡面貼身穿著的。<em>Kutoneth</em> 通常被譯作「束腰長襯衫」或「內袍」（“tunic”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New English Bible (1970)\">NEB</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Bible (1970)\">NAB</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> ）。在許多語言中，「襯衫」（“shirt”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）會是最接近的對等詞。根據<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:4\">EXO 28:4</a> 的描述，內袍是「帶刺繡的」（“embroidered”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）。關於「帶刺繡的」一詞的翻譯，參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.5.3.11 繡花布、刺繡作品 (embroidered cloth, needlework)&lt;REALIA:1.5.3.11&gt;</a> 。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
